    "title_en": "SU(4) Heisenberg model on the hyperhoneycomb lattice",
    "abstract_en": "We study the ground state of the SU(4) Heisenberg model on the hyperhoneycomb lattice using three-dimensional projected entangled pair states. We show that it is possible to compute physical observables for the ground states using loop expansions, which converge quickly on tree-like lattices. Our extrapolations to the limit of infinite bond dimensions point toward gapless spin-liquid ground state.",
